    <title>Hexo 시작하기</title>
    <link href="https://snowrain10.github.io/2020/03/16/Getting-Started-with-Hexo/"/>
    <id>https://snowrain10.github.io/2020/03/16/Getting-Started-with-Hexo/</id>
    <published>2020-03-16T10:51:51.000Z</published>
    <updated>2020-03-16T11:59:54.501Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>참고 사이트<br><a href="https://futurecreator.github.io/2016/06/14/get-started-with-hexo/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">워드프레스보다 쉬운 Hexo 블로그 시작하기</a></p><h4 id="설치하기"><a href="#설치하기" class="headerlink" title="설치하기"></a>설치하기</h4><ul><li><a href="https://nodejs.org/ko/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Node.js</a> 와 <a href="https://git-scm.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Git</a> 설치</li><li>npm 으로 hexo 설치</li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ npm install -g hexo-cli</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="블로그-파일을-저장할-폴더를-만들고-구조-생성하기"><a href="#블로그-파일을-저장할-폴더를-만들고-구조-생성하기" class="headerlink" title="블로그 파일을 저장할 폴더를 만들고 구조 생성하기"></a>블로그 파일을 저장할 폴더를 만들고 구조 생성하기</h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo init myBlog</span><br><span class="line">$ <span class="built_in">cd</span> myBlog</span><br><span class="line">$ npm install</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>생성된 폴더 구조</li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">. <span class="comment"># 블로그 루트 폴더</span></span><br><span class="line">├─ .gitignore</span><br><span class="line">├─ _config.yml <span class="comment"># 설정 파일</span></span><br><span class="line">├─ node_modules</span><br><span class="line">├─ package.json</span><br><span class="line">├─ scaffolds <span class="comment"># 스캐폴드(양식)</span></span><br><span class="line">├─ <span class="built_in">source</span> <span class="comment"># 소스 폴더</span></span><br><span class="line">|  ├─ _drafts <span class="comment"># 초안 # 안보이는데...</span></span><br><span class="line">|  └─ _posts <span class="comment"># 포스트</span></span><br><span class="line">└─ themes <span class="comment"># 테마 폴더</span></span><br><span class="line">   └─ landscape <span class="comment"># 기본 테마</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="로컬서버-띄우기"><a href="#로컬서버-띄우기" class="headerlink" title="로컬서버 띄우기"></a>로컬서버 띄우기</h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">INFO  Start processing</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Hexo is running at http://localhost:4000 . Press Ctrl+C to stop.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="로컬서버-접속하기"><a href="#로컬서버-접속하기" class="headerlink" title="로컬서버 접속하기"></a>로컬서버 접속하기</h4><p>위에서 나온 주소 <a href="http://localhost:4000/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">localhost:4000</a>에 접속한다.</p><p>포트를 변경하려면 옵션 -P를 준다.</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo server -p 3000</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
